quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  68,34,Yaqeenan khuda-tars logon ke liye unke Rubb ke yahan niyamat bhari jannatein hain
  68,35,Kya hum farma-bardaaron ka haal mujreemon sa kardein
  68,36,"Tum logon ko kya ho gaya hai, tum kaise hukum lagate ho"
  68,37,Kya tumhare paas koi kitaab hai jismein tum yeh padhte ho
  68,38,Ke tumhare liye zaroor wahan wahi kuch hai jo tum apne liye pasand karte ho
  68,39,Ya phir kya tumhare liye roz-e-qayamat tak humpar kuch ahad-o-paiman (covenant) sabit hai ke tumhein wahi kuch milega jiska tum hukum lagao
  68,40,Inse pucho tum mein se kaun iska zaamin (gurantee/responsible) hai
  68,41,Ya phir inke thehraye huye kuch sahreek hain (jinhon ne iska zimma liya ho)?yeh baat hai to layein apne shareekon ko agar yeh sacchey hain
  68,42,Jis roz sakht waqt aa padega aur logon ko sajda karne ke liye bulaya jayega to yeh log sajda na kar sakenge
  68,43,"Inki nigaahein nichey hongi, zillat inpar chaa rahi hogi. Yeh jab sahi-o-saalim thay us waqt inhein sajde ke liye (bulaya jata tha) aur yeh inkar karte thay"
  68,44,"Pas aey Nabi, tum is kalam ke jhutlane walon ka maamla mujhpar chodh do hum aise tarike se inko batadreej tabahi ki taraf le jayenge ke inko khabar bhi na hogi"
  68,45,"Main inki rassi daraaz kar raha hoon, meri chaal badi zabardast hai"
  68,46,Kya tum insey koi ajar (compensation) talab kar rahey ho ke yeh is chatti ke bojh (feel burdened with debt) taley dabey ja rahe hoon
  68,47,Kya inke paas gaib ka ilam hai jisey yeh likh rahey hon
  68,48,"Pas apne Rubb ka faisla saadir honay tak sabr karo aur machli wale (younis) ki tarah na ho jao, jab usne pukara tha aur woh gham se bhara hua tha"
  68,49,Agar uske Rubb ki meharbani uske shamil-e-haal na ho jati to woh mazmoom (disgrace) hokar chatyal maidan mein phenk diya jata
  68,50,Aakhir-e-kaar uske Rubb ne usey barguzida (exalted) farma liya aur usey saleh bandon mein shamil kardiya
  68,51,"Jab yeh kafir log kalam-e-nasihat (Quran) sunte hain to tumhein aisi nazaron se dekhte hain ke goya tumhare qadam ukhaad denge, Aur kehte hain ke yeh zaroor deewana hai"
  68,52,Halaanke yeh to sarey jahaan walon ke liye ek naseehat hai